      "webPublicationDate":"2013-11-03T18:22:17Z",
      "webTitle":"Energy bills: npower amassed £400m credit from customers",
      "webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/money/2013/nov/03/energy-bills-npower-400m-credit-customers",
